Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.32,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}未來一定就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:04.00,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}所以邁開步伐啟程吧
