Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:33.23,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}難為情的部分和迷茫一起扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:36.74,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}剩下的只有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:43.45,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}無論從哪個角度去看
